Type: Package
Package: downscalr
Title: Downscaling land-use change projections
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Krisztin", "Tamás", , "krisztin@iiasa.ac.at", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Wögerer", "Michael", , "wogerer@iiasa.ac.at", role = "aut"),
    person("Ringwald", "Leopold", , "ringwald@iiasa.ac.at", role = "aut")
  )
Maintainer: Tamás Krisztin <krisztin@iiasa.ac.at>
Description: For high-resolution projections of future land-use change
    IAMs often rely on downscaled projections. This package provides
    econometric models for prior estimation and a flexible, transparent
    and easy to use framework to downscale such projections.
